data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled colonial, just a couple minutes walk from Downtown Dexter. Fully Remodeled inside and out, and needs absolutely nothing. Move right in and enjoy a quaint, cozy, and convenient experience With 3 bedrooms upstairs and a his and hers bathroom, kitchen, living room, and dinning room on the first floor.  Everything is less than 2 years old, including the central air unit and a freshly poured driveway... Schedule your showing ASAP because this property is priced thousands below market value with 1 bedroom condos directly across the street starting in the mid 300's
